DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Burke-Gilman Trail. \nWe’ll be rooting out non-native grasses that are trying to smother the many native wild flowers we have planted there. \nRegister to meet.
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/more-weed-removal-at-the-pollinator-patch/
