LAST-MODIFIED:20260302T194736Z
UID:230256-1773334800-1773352800@www.seattleparksfoundation.org
SUMMARY:Brewing Hope at Stoup Brewing in Ballard
DESCRIPTION:Join Seattle Parks Foundation at Stoup Brewing in Ballard on March 12! \nFrom 5-10 pm\, $1 from every pint will be donated back to parks and public projects! Brewing Hope is Stoup’s pint night program to support nonprofits making a difference. We are grateful to be their spotlighted organization in March. Buy a local brew and support parks to grow a greener community together! \nVisit Stoup’s website
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/brewing-hope-at-stoup-brewing-in-ballard/
LOCATION:Stoup Brewing\, 1108 NW 52nd Street\, Seattle\, WA\, 98107\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/stoup-giveback.png
END:VEVENT
