SUMMARY:First glimpses of Spring in St. Mark's Greenbelt
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at St. Mark’s Greenbelt \nAs spring approaches help us remove plants that are not endemic to the Pacific NW\, but seem to be due to their aggressive growth habits. \nRegister
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/first-glimpses-of-the-coming-spring/
